data.description: 4 bedroom, 2 bath country home.  This home features a very inviting open floorplan for family and friend gathers, with a separate living and family room.  The backyard is also very inviting with mature landscaping, a deck, a cute shed that can be used as a potting shed or kids playhouse, and not to mention a new metal storage shed with overhead doors on both ends.  This home also qualifies for a VA assumable loan with a low interest rate.
